399
00:30:22,400 --> 00:30:24,270
Dia sudah memiliki kemampuan persepsi abadi.

400
00:30:24,270 --> 00:30:26,030
Saat ini dia berada di Perkumpulan Wushuang,

401
00:30:26,030 --> 00:30:27,290
tapi besok mungkin saja

402
00:30:27,480 --> 00:30:29,240
membelot ke sekte-sekte abadi.

403
00:30:32,360 --> 00:30:33,560
Bukankah Sekte Qinghong?

404
00:30:33,720 --> 00:30:34,790
Sekte abadi?

405
00:30:35,200 --> 00:30:36,350
Sekte Qinghong

406
00:30:38,240 --> 00:30:39,590
